*Razlika* između ljudi i životinja je u tome što ljudi imaju razvijenu sposobnost razmišljanja. (The difference between humans and animals is that humans have developed the ability to think.)

*Razlikovati* se od drugih je važno za uspeh. (Distinguishing oneself from others is important for success.)

On je jednom rekao da ne može da *razlikuje* dobro od lošeg. (He once said that he can't tell the difference between good and bad.)

Oni su otkrili veliku *razliku* između njihovih metoda. (They discovered a big difference between their methods.)

Oni su morali da *razlikuju* između dva terena. (They had to distinguish between two fields.)